quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  39,64,"Say [O Prophet], “Do you order me to worship other than Allah, O ignorant people?”"
  39,65,"It has already been revealed to you and to those who came before you that if you associate others with Allah, your deeds will surely become worthless, and you will certainly be among the losers"
  39,66,"Rather, worship Allah alone and be among those who are grateful"
  39,67,"They did not revere Allah His true reverence. On the Day of Resurrection, the whole earth will be in His Grip, and the heavens will be rolled up in His Right Hand. Glorified and exalted is He above all what they associate with Him"
  39,68,"The Trumpet will be blown and all those in the heavens and all those on earth will fall dead, except whom Allah wills. Then it will be blown again, and at once they will be standing, looking on"
  39,69,"The earth will shine with the light of its Lord, the record of deeds will be placed, the prophets and the witnesses will be brought forth, and judgment will be passed between them with fairness, and they will not be wronged"
  39,70,"Every soul will be paid in full for what it has done, for He knows best what they do"